I always felt like

00:32:29.428 --> 00:32:32.556
you were looking for someone else in me.

00:32:34.767 --> 00:32:36.894
At the end of your gaze,

00:32:37.811 --> 00:32:40.022
it was always the chief.

00:32:41.273 --> 00:32:42.107
As if…

00:32:44.234 --> 00:32:45.068
she were a child

00:32:46.737 --> 00:32:48.030
you left behind and couldn't forget.

