Still, I feel encouraged.

00:55:57.126 --> 00:55:58.335
Thank you for the compliment.

00:55:59.503 --> 00:56:01.463
Mr. Lim Hyeon-jun, do you like me?

00:56:07.636 --> 00:56:08.971
Goodbye, bro.

