00:56:23.360 --> 00:56:25.154
Well, I guess I wasn't thinking straight!

00:56:27.907 --> 00:56:28.908
Hey.

00:56:28.991 --> 00:56:31.243
Can you wear the sneakers
your ex-girlfriend bought for you?

