Yeah, of course.
The sneakers aren't to blame.

00:56:33.787 --> 00:56:34.622
But how?

00:56:34.705 --> 00:56:37.333
You'd be reminded of her
every time you wear them.

00:56:37.416 --> 00:56:38.417
It's human nature to forget.

00:56:39.001 --> 00:56:41.420
It's hard at first,
but it fades away after a while.

00:56:41.503 --> 00:56:43.255
Bad feelings are temporary,

00:56:43.339 --> 00:56:44.840
